265
00:13:34,916 --> 00:13:36,208
My darling Yuki is safe.

266
00:13:36,291 --> 00:13:37,833
That's all that matters to me.

267
00:13:37,916 --> 00:13:41,208
Now, be a good boy
and untie me, kay?

268
00:13:43,333 --> 00:13:45,041
Come on.

269
00:13:45,458 --> 00:13:47,375
Look at me, Yuki.

270
00:13:47,458 --> 00:13:48,625
I can't.

271
