I had to keep you safe!

281
00:14:11,958 --> 00:14:15,000
I can't protect you with
my hands like this, Yuki!

282
00:14:17,916 --> 00:14:19,000
Okay.

283
00:14:19,083 --> 00:14:21,291
End of the line, kid.

284
00:14:21,375 --> 00:14:22,208
This is it.

285
00:14:22,291 --> 00:14:23,375
I'm gonna die here.

286
00:14:23,458 --> 00:14:24,750
Yuki, can you read me?

287
00:14:24,833 --> 00:14:26,208
Come in, Yuki!

288
00:14:26,291 --> 00:14:27,500
