and hope for the best.

291
00:14:35,958 --> 00:14:37,000
Son of a--!

292
00:14:37,083 --> 00:14:39,291
The reception's for
balls up in here!

293
00:14:39,625 --> 00:14:40,708
Awesome!

294
00:14:40,791 --> 00:14:42,958
The cell-phone tower's
out of commission.

295
00:14:43,041 --> 00:14:46,500
Meanwhile, I've got a working
diary and a big knife.

296
00:14:46,583 --> 00:14:48,750
