off or something!

297
00:14:53,041 --> 00:14:54,500
Wouldn't you know it.

298
00:14:54,583 --> 00:14:56,041
They jammed our phones.

299
00:14:56,125 --> 00:14:57,791
Typical.

300
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,791
All that running around
was bad for my do, anyway.

301
00:15:01,875 --> 00:15:02,791
Yeah.

302
00:15:02,875 --> 00:15:04,458
