my makeup, too.

303
00:15:04,541 --> 00:15:06,041
Might as well ditch them.

304
00:15:06,125 --> 00:15:07,666
They ain't gonna help us.

305
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,083
Adios, useless diary.

306
00:15:12,583 --> 00:15:13,750
That's a good thing.

307
00:15:13,833 --> 00:15:16,333
