308
00:15:18,833 --> 00:15:27,000
Wait a sec... are those?!

309
00:15:27,083 --> 00:15:30,250
Pardon my French, kiddies,
but you all are fucked!

310
00:15:30,333 --> 00:15:32,291
"I don't understand it,
Marco how did you know

311
00:15:32,375 --> 00:15:34,750
we were gonna destroy
your diaries?!" Simple!

312
00:15:34,833 --> 00:15:36,250
'Cause we're smarter than you!

313
