00:15:38,041 --> 00:15:40,500
and now you're
gonna pay the price!

315
00:15:41,166 --> 00:15:43,708
Oh yeah!

316
00:15:43,791 --> 00:15:47,041
Guess I'll give you the formal
introduction before I kill you.

317
00:15:47,125 --> 00:15:49,250
I am Seventh!

318
00:15:49,333 --> 00:15:51,250
Marco Ikusaba!

319
00:15:51,333 --> 00:15:52,833
I'm Seventh, also.

320
00:15:52,916 --> 00:15:54,166
Ai Mikami.

321
00:15:54,250 --> 00:15:57,375
[BOTH] Our Exchange Diaries
are the real deal!

322
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:00,291
--Game over, chumps!
--Game over, chumps!

323
00:16:00,375 --> 00:16:02,458
They're actual keepers!

324
00:16:03,333 --> 00:16:04,166
Yuki, please!

325
00:16:04,250 --> 00:16:06,125
I am begging you to untie me!

326
00:16:06,208 --> 00:16:08,875
I'll never take you
prisoner again I swear it!

327
00:16:08,958 --> 00:16:11,041
I swear on my life!

328
00:16:11,125 --> 00:16:14,375
I adore you with all of
my heart, Yukiteru Amano!

329
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,416
Just this once believe in me!

330
00:16:18,083 --> 00:16:19,583
I can't set her free!

331
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:22,500
She belongs in a
damn straightjacket!

332
00:16:23,083 --> 00:16:25,750
But, if I don't set her free

333
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:28,208
then we're talking
two against one.

334
00:16:28,791 --> 00:16:31,125
And that one's
quick with a knife!

335
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:33,958
God, are the girls
even alive down there?!

336
00:16:34,375 --> 00:16:35,750
I got to live.

337
00:16:35,833 --> 00:16:37,708
Whatever it takes!

338
00:16:37,791 --> 00:16:39,833
I got to win!

339
00:16:43,416 --> 00:16:45,083
Give me the knife.

340
00:16:46,958 --> 00:16:48,750
I love you, too.

341
00:16:48,833 --> 00:16:49,416
Well?

342
00:16:49,500 --> 00:16:50,833
Fair enough.

343
00:16:50,916 --> 00:16:53,541
We don't have a problem
taking you out first, girlie.

344
00:16:57,541 --> 00:16:59,166
Tell me something kiddo.

345
00:16:59,250 --> 00:17:03,000
Do you believe in the
all-redeeming power of love?

346
00:17:04,250 --> 00:17:06,708
My Future Diary is
a testament to our love.

347
00:17:06,791 --> 00:17:10,291
It keeps tabs on my baby,
so I can protect her 24-7.

348
00:17:10,375 --> 00:17:13,041
Meanwhile, my Future Diary
keeps tabs on him.

349
00:17:13,125 --> 00:17:16,583
I've got Marco's fine-ass
backside, and he's got mine.

350
00:17:16,916 --> 00:17:18,791
By the power of
our phones combined.

351
00:17:18,875 --> 00:17:23,125
Behold the bad-assery
of true frigging love!

352
00:17:24,041 --> 00:17:26,250
Uh, congrats?

353
00:17:26,333 --> 00:17:27,916
Do I have to
spell it out for you?

354
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:31,250
This is gonna be a rumble
between couples, a love match!

355
00:17:31,333 --> 00:17:35,041
And our love has steamrolled way
worse than the two of you!

356
00:17:35,708 --> 00:17:38,541
This ain't gonna take long if
you guys just stand there!

357
00:17:40,708 --> 00:17:42,625
Don't throw knives
at my beloved.

358
00:17:42,708 --> 00:17:43,541
Whoa.

359
00:17:43,625 --> 00:17:45,291
That was amazing!

360
00:17:46,208 --> 00:17:47,750
How about two at once?!

361
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:53,041
Yuki said I was amazing!

362
00:17:53,125 --> 00:17:54,500
What the hell?!

363
00:17:54,583 --> 00:17:56,208
Impossible!

364
00:17:59,333 --> 00:18:00,958
One compliment from
Yuki and I feel like I could

365
00:18:01,041 --> 00:18:03,583
deflect these knives all day
long without even trying!

366
00:18:03,666 --> 00:18:05,125
You're doing such a great job!

367
00:18:05,208 --> 00:18:06,375
Just keep it up!

368
00:18:07,083 --> 00:18:08,125
Hey lover.

369
00:18:08,208 --> 00:18:09,958
Don't panic,
but I'm fresh outta shivs.

370
00:18:10,041 --> 00:18:10,791
What?

371
00:18:10,875 --> 00:18:12,166
Already?!

372
00:18:13,666 --> 00:18:14,500
I'm doing great!

373
00:18:14,583 --> 00:18:15,791
Yuki said so!

374
00:18:15,875 --> 00:18:17,375
--Uh-oh.
--Uh-oh.

375
00:18:18,666 --> 00:18:22,500
Hold onto your asses!

376
00:18:22,583 --> 00:18:23,583
--Bye!
--Bye!

377
00:18:24,541 --> 00:18:26,208
Huh?!

378
00:18:29,958 --> 00:18:32,166
Hinata and Mao are gone!

379
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:44,083
Why'd you drag us out here?

380
00:18:44,166 --> 00:18:45,916
I can drag you
back in if ya want...

381
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,500
but it's gonna get hot in there.

382
00:18:47,583 --> 00:18:49,916
I don't think that's
what you want.

383
00:18:51,625 --> 00:18:53,458
Here it comes.

384
00:18:55,541 --> 00:18:57,458
Just in case we
didn't seal the deal

385
00:18:57,541 --> 00:19:00,500
our pal Ta had orders
to torch the place.

386
00:19:00,583 --> 00:19:02,416
Ai...
Let's book.

387
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:05,041
That's it?
You're just running away?

388
00:19:05,125 --> 00:19:06,958
Who said anything about running?

389
00:19:07,041 --> 00:19:10,166
We still got to
school those poseurs!

390
00:19:15,208 --> 00:19:16,750
The girls are in danger!

391
00:19:16,833 --> 00:19:19,291
I have to rescue
them from Seventh!

392
00:19:19,958 --> 00:19:21,125
But...

393
00:19:21,666 --> 00:19:23,208
Is it okay to use Yuno?

394
00:19:23,291 --> 00:19:25,416
I mean, can I trust her?

395
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:27,458
You can use me all you want.

396
00:19:28,875 --> 00:19:31,250
Bet you you're wondering
if that's safe, but it is.

397
00:19:31,333 --> 00:19:33,916
I'll even tell you
how to sell me on it.

398
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:36,166
"Help me save those
other girls, Yuno.

399
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:40,166
And I'll pretend to be your
boyfriend, just like before."

400
00:19:42,416 --> 00:19:43,291
Okay, then.

401
00:19:43,375 --> 00:19:44,708
I can do pretend.

402
00:19:44,791 --> 00:19:47,291
Hell, it's not like
I have a choice.

403
00:19:49,583 --> 00:19:51,208
I accept.

404
00:19:51,625 --> 00:19:53,333
Time for round two!

405
00:19:53,416 --> 00:19:55,958
Did you think we
were giving up that easy?

406
00:20:00,041 --> 00:20:01,333
Yuno!

407
00:20:01,416 --> 00:20:02,833
Ai!

408
00:20:05,541 --> 00:20:07,458
Once I turn you and your
boyfriend inside out,

409
00:20:07,541 --> 00:20:08,875
Yuki will love me!

410
00:20:08,958 --> 00:20:10,958
What the hell is
wrong with you?!

411
00:20:32,333 --> 00:20:33,916
What just happened?

412
00:20:41,041 --> 00:20:42,375
Yuno!

413
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:45,541
Yuno.

414
00:20:45,625 --> 00:20:46,375
Please!

415
00:20:46,458 --> 00:20:47,875
Wake up!

416
00:20:50,416 --> 00:20:53,250
Why didn't you help
your woman, you little punk?

417
00:20:57,666 --> 00:20:59,125
When a girl is in trouble.

418
00:20:59,208 --> 00:21:00,583
you jump through
fire and if there's

419
00:21:00,666 --> 00:21:02,583
