421
00:21:04,291 --> 00:21:05,541
Huh?!

422
00:21:07,458 --> 00:21:08,875
No, it's not my fault.

423
00:21:08,958 --> 00:21:10,041
She told me.

424
00:21:10,125 --> 00:21:11,750
I could use her.

425
00:21:12,458 --> 00:21:13,750
You're a waste of oxygen.

426
00:21:13,833 --> 00:21:15,375
You know that don't you?

427
00:21:15,458 --> 00:21:17,125
No, it isn't my fault!

428
00:21:17,208 --> 00:21:20,208
I know it was cowardly to
hang back the way I did!

429
00:21:20,291 --> 00:21:22,083
I know it was!

430
00:21:22,166 --> 00:21:23,250
But I...

431
00:21:23,333 --> 00:21:24,750
I can't!

432
00:21:24,833 --> 00:21:27,166
I'm just too weak!

433
00:21:29,458 --> 00:21:31,583
Go to hell.

434
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:43,583
Our plan was all for naught.

435
00:21:43,666 --> 00:21:45,708
Yuki and Yuno's
diaries were taken

436
00:21:45,791 --> 00:21:47,875
as spoils of battle by Seventh.

437
00:21:48,250 --> 00:21:50,625
Yuno's been unconscious
ever since the ordeal.

438
00:21:50,708 --> 00:21:53,625
And Hinata and Mao
were both badly injured.

439
00:21:53,708 --> 00:21:56,625
This round proved to be
a resounding failure.

440
00:21:56,708 --> 00:21:59,416
At least the firefighters made
good time getting there.

441
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:03,250
A minute more and we'd have lost
you both to smoke-inhalation.

442
00:22:04,416 --> 00:22:05,666
Sir.

443
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:08,458
I came to take a quick
look at your head injury.

444
00:22:08,541 --> 00:22:11,708
