you receive it, anyway?

445
00:22:12,083 --> 00:22:13,000
Man?

446
00:22:13,083 --> 00:22:14,000
Woman?

447
00:22:14,083 --> 00:22:15,333
Both?

448
00:22:15,416 --> 00:22:17,500
